  <span id="freeText5316347123830692731" style="display:none"><b>A masterpiece of breathtaking scope—a brilliantly conceived epic novel that traces the entire turbulent course of English history.</b><br /> <br />This rich tapestry weaves a compelling saga of five families—the Wilsons, the Masons, the family of Porteus, the Shockleys, and the Godfreys—who reflect the changing character of Britain. <br /><br />As their fates and fortunes intertwine over the course of the centuries, their greater destinies offer a fascinating glimpse into the future. <br /><br />An absorbing historical chronicle, Sarum is a keen tale of struggle and adventure, a profound human drama, and a magnificent work of sheer storytelling.</span>
