    <a title="Viv Bearne" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/7357085-viv-bearne"><img alt="Viv Bearne" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1326964277p2/7357085.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/257559510?book_show_action=true">Jan 06, 2012</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Viv Bearne" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Viv Bearne" href="/user/show/7357085-viv-bearne">Viv Bearne</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Hardcover 9780517223543" href="/book/show/92163.Sarum">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer257559510" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17347234085219636361">Sarum is my all time favorite book, coming from the south west of England myself it is my history and so much research has gone into it. Many if not all of the great structures are still standing. A great read</span>

          </span>
        </div>


